Insider Activity


Individual




Bruce G. Bodaken



Mr. Bruce G. Bodaken is Independent Director at Rite-Aid Corp., Independent Director at WageWorks, Inc., and a Director-Value & Science Driven Healthcare at Institute of Medicine. He is on the Board of Directors at AltheaDx, Inc., Rite-Aid Corp., WageWorks, Inc., and California Business Roundtable.
Mr. Bodaken was previously employed as Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Blue Shield of California, Senior VP & Associate Chief Operating Officer by FHP, Inc., Chairman by Blue Shield of California Life & Health Insurance Co., and Senior VP & Associate Chief Operating Officer by FHP International Corp. He also served on the board at America's Health Insurance Plans, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Colorado State University and a graduate degree from The University of Colorado.



